---
title: Creamy Chicken, Mushroom & Truffle Fettuccine with Tomato-Rocket Salad
description: This fettuccine dish pairs the earthy flavour of mushroom, chicken and truffle with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the richness of the pasta with peppery rocket and sharp Parmesan.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652771f63f89ff19ac8446a2-032bbff6.jpeg
